<body>
<div class="column">
<h1 class="main-color">
tearoom
</h1>
<p>
Fancy a cuppa?
</p>
<p>
Let the world know about the tech event you are hosting.
By simply submitting the details of your tech event to tearoom, you will get
lots of coders and people interested in tech join in the party.
</p>

<form action="/events" method="POST" class="main-color">

  What:
<input type="textbox" name="eventName" style="color:#888; width:200px;" value="Name of Your Event" onfocus="this.value=''" onblur="inputBlur(this)" />
  <br><br>

  <div>
  <div>Who:</div>
  <div><input type="textbox" name="organisation" style="color:#888; width:200px;" value="Name of Your Organisation" onfocus="this.value=''" onblur="inputBlur(this)">

  <br>
  <input type="textbox" name="organisation" style="color:#888; width:200px;" value="Who Can Attend" onfocus="this.value=''" onblur="inputBlur(this)">
  </div></div>
  <br>

  Why:
  <input type="textbox" name="summary" style="color:#888; width:200px;" value="Tell Us a Bit about It" onfocus="this.value=''" onblur="inputBlur(this)">
  <br><br>

  When:
  <input type="textbox" name="date" style="color:#888; width:200px;" value="Date & Time" onfocus="this.value=''" onblur="inputBlur(this)">
  <br><br>

  Where:
  <input type="textbox" name="place" style="color:#888; width:200px;" value="Location" onfocus="this.value=''" onblur="inputBlur(this)">
  <br><br>

  Contact:
  <input type="textbox" name="contact" style="color:#888; width:200px;" value="Info Email" onfocus="this.value=''" onblur="inputBlur(this)">
  <br><br>

  <input type="submit" name="submitButton" value="Submit Your Event!">
  </form>
  <p>
  Please contact tearoom if you have any questions or queries.
  </p>
